                    },
                    "body": "See reference guide http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.application.html.\r\n\r\nFor baseUrl set in the application.ini and need call the resource frontcontroller.\r\n\r\nresources.frontcontroller.baseUrl = \"<value>\"",
