                    "body": "The guide is very clear, but nothing forces me to avoid the using of the variable application in the config.ini  LIKE\r\n\r\napplication.variableName = \"variableValue\"\r\n\r\nIn the guide nothing is mentioned about it.\r\n\r\n",
